{"tid":635873,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點解佛教值得人尊重?","createTime":"2018-04-20T11:33:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-04T10:53:00.000Z","uid":58069,"like":155,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"a2fc6ba19239cfa20d29b4fac964a4bc6d6e4ed0","tid":635873,"uid":58069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T11:33:42.000Z","msg":"1. 佛教從唔會逼人信，你唔信都冇野，唔會因為咁而受難。<br />\n反觀其他教，唔信就落地獄，殺撚晒人只要臨死前信教，就冇事上天堂爽皮。<br />\n<br />\n2.佛教存在最終目的係導人向善，無論佛教講既野係真係假都好，佢用因果報黎希望人地可以做更多好事。盡量減少自己的利慾，感受世界。反觀其他教有冇係導人向善就見仁見智，而係想排除異教徒，唔比任何教派同存。<br />\n<br />\n3.佛教咁長歷史但係冇因為傳教同權力問題產生導致大屠殺，就算有，都係好少野。藏傳佛教，印度佛教，中國佛教都好，起碼冇殘殺同類。再睇下伊斯蘭教同埋耶教，分開十幾個教派日日殺人搶野。舉個例，十字軍東征:這是一系列在羅馬天主教教皇的准許下的戰役，由西歐的封建領主和騎士對他們認為是異教徒的國家（地中海東岸）發動了持續近200年的宗教戰爭。唔止冇咩戰爭，佛教連殺生都唔鼓吹，食素，連動物都包容埋。<br />\n<br />\n4.垃圾教徒呃神騙鬼周圍都有，貪僧都會有，有人類存在就無可避免。但係有冇虛偽到變童咁撚痴線?<br />\n<br />\n5.佛教個世界可能吹得好大，但起碼<span style=\"color: red;\">經義之間</span>講得通，六道，因果，起碼你唔理現實世界咁睇，佢可以冇咩FAIL位。<br />\n再睇下聖經，個神又話全善又點，有心叫大衛出賣耶穌，等佢比人罵2000年。咁姐係玩鳩大衛?耶穌受難死撚左，明明就係上天堂同呀神父子樂，又講到佢贖罪。再求其比個例子 約翰福音 20:17 耶穌說、<span style=\"color: red;\">不要摸我</span>．因我還沒有升上去見我的父．你往我弟兄那裡去、告訴他們說、我要升上去、見我的父、也是你們的父．見我的　神、也是你們的　神。<br />\n路加福音<br />\n24:39 你們看我的手、我的腳、就知道實在是我了．<span style=\"color: red;\">摸我看看</span>．魂無骨無肉、你們看我是有的。<br />\n你老母姐係摸唔摸得????<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又話神全能，姐係神知道人會食善惡果喇，又姐係有心玩鳩我地，就發脾氣趕我地走伊甸園。矛盾到仆街<br />\n<br />\n利申，咩教都唔信，冇研究過宗教，唔信咩因果點點點，聖經點點點，但係佛教起碼真係可以做到導人向善呢樣最基本既野，入面既野吹得幾大又好，係真係假，因此就值得受人尊重。另外我尊重任何因為宗教而向世界貢獻既人。"},{"pid":"11f3bae09eb849c45d737ae0f95cb2990afba5a0","tid":635873,"uid":41355,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T11:39:07.000Z","msg":"要同耶教對比的話幾乎咩都好過耶教，我建議都係客觀啲看待佛教/佛學<br />\n<br />\n問翻幾個問題，<br />\n<br />\n1.信佛/學佛有咩著數同缺點?<br />\n<br />\n2.佛家思想是否厭世?<br />\n<br />\n3.人人都應該學佛?<br />\n<br />\n4.佛所教授的道理正確嗎?"},{"pid":"4cdaab9b957c6f2c91501ca106e2a1e3f0a42b97","tid":635873,"uid":52362,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T12:03:21.000Z","msg":"係猶大啊ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"337a46415bde56d010d5c5d0973530bc583ca040","tid":635873,"uid":173852,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T12:20:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 轉頭又到耶撚被批鬥  耶撚真慘"},{"pid":"c7fc82cd3d4b7f37ba1cdc822619ed0dd78fc46b","tid":635873,"uid":48796,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T12:22:21.000Z","msg":"約伯記, 忠心耿耿就要畀神撚狗撚到冚家剷 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PXT3T-hsKsc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DPXT3T-hsKsc&d=F7LzYusczQOdPG6krgBM07IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=2c9bede4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PXT3T-hsKsc</a>"},{"pid":"d0dc05bd0f23b42dffafb986e9ad46e2307d1fd2","tid":635873,"uid":54927,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T12:24:33.000Z","msg":"同我老豆講既野一樣<br />\n導人向善就得 唔使你日日口掛住大仁大義<br />\n知道做壞事有報應 存好心做好事就得"},{"pid":"01a1298fffc7d794f6ddf3ff49e6c57e397f899a","tid":635873,"uid":54927,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T12:25:14.000Z","msg":"寫聖經嗰班仆街都唔知係唔係讀寫障<br />\n寫野1999 語句鳩下鳩下"},{"pid":"8c10a166ae7a0e54cf09d0980fa61ab18a7d5ae3","tid":635873,"uid":15371,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T12:31:15.000Z","msg":"其他教=耶<br />\nChing sick ball"},{"pid":"bef39d62fe014b583fe5663e8f19c3557fcf8adb","tid":635873,"uid":130378,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"01a1298fffc7d794f6ddf3ff49e6c57e397f899a","tid":635873,"uid":54927,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T12:25:14.000Z","msg":"寫聖經嗰班仆街都唔知係唔係讀寫障<br />\n寫野1999 語句鳩下鳩下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T13:51:12.000Z","msg":"修改聖經嘅係以前有權力有地位嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ad82ad3944dd7b92eced27f7e251fc3bf71b207","tid":635873,"uid":28264,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T20:33:39.000Z","msg":"藏傳佛教冇?<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你不如去了解下藏傳佛教既歷史先<br />\n藏傳佛教本來係4個分支 呢架一支獨大 <br />\n你不如去了解下原因先<br />\n<br />\n利申 認同佛教值得人尊重 只係樓d既例子錯"},{"pid":"a6aff91a47b758e5c15d32516ba5d885e95cf5ee","tid":635873,"uid":24345,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T20:38:50.000Z","msg":"拎十字軍東征我覺得有少少問題，痴撚住伊斯蘭好難唔打返轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係伊斯蘭入侵歐洲先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同緬甸一樣佛都有火屠殺羅興亞人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14c7ff6e986bd72bd8cb7a50bc62ef0c9fdd4435","tid":635873,"uid":108090,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"a6aff91a47b758e5c15d32516ba5d885e95cf5ee","tid":635873,"uid":24345,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T20:38:50.000Z","msg":"拎十字軍東征我覺得有少少問題，痴撚住伊斯蘭好難唔打返轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係伊斯蘭入侵歐洲先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同緬甸一樣佛都有火屠殺羅興亞人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T20:46:53.000Z","msg":"別人打你的左臉<br />\n把右臉也給他打<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70c655924070a707116273d07bd42a56a784107f","tid":635873,"uid":9269,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"11f3bae09eb849c45d737ae0f95cb2990afba5a0","tid":635873,"uid":41355,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T11:39:07.000Z","msg":"要同耶教對比的話幾乎咩都好過耶教，我建議都係客觀啲看待佛教/佛學<br />\n<br />\n問翻幾個問題，<br />\n<br />\n1.信佛/學佛有咩著數同缺點?<br />\n<br />\n2.佛家思想是否厭世?<br />\n<br />\n3.人人都應該學佛?<br />\n<br />\n4.佛所教授的道理正確嗎?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T20:52:03.000Z","msg":"1. 佛本來就唔會講咩著數唔著數，缺點唔缺點，有緣有慧根咪信，呢d偽命題一念之間<br />\n<br />\n2. 如果信輪迴既，心善做功德，咁算正能量定厭世<br />\n<br />\n3. 與佛有因與佛有緣<br />\n<br />\n4. 我都答你唔到。其他宗教所教授的道理又正確嗎<br />\n<br />\n利申：食肉飲酒，啪啪啪，有錯漏歡迎屌"},{"pid":"76a370f55b51bca81b04327611d764a64bc35cd3","tid":635873,"uid":33539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T21:11:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b58c816185d2728a3654bd35c8a018bc1ec140b","tid":635873,"uid":82717,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"11f3bae09eb849c45d737ae0f95cb2990afba5a0","tid":635873,"uid":41355,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T11:39:07.000Z","msg":"要同耶教對比的話幾乎咩都好過耶教，我建議都係客觀啲看待佛教/佛學<br />\n<br />\n問翻幾個問題，<br />\n<br />\n1.信佛/學佛有咩著數同缺點?<br />\n<br />\n2.佛家思想是否厭世?<br />\n<br />\n3.人人都應該學佛?<br />\n<br />\n4.佛所教授的道理正確嗎?"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T22:34:52.000Z","msg":"佛教咁無生產力又無乜建樹都好?"},{"pid":"baf1bcd9c53e9212648aada57f995beecd67b770","tid":635873,"uid":41355,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"3b58c816185d2728a3654bd35c8a018bc1ec140b","tid":635873,"uid":82717,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"11f3bae09eb849c45d737ae0f95cb2990afba5a0","tid":635873,"uid":41355,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T11:39:07.000Z","msg":"要同耶教對比的話幾乎咩都好過耶教，我建議都係客觀啲看待佛教/佛學<br />\n<br />\n問翻幾個問題，<br />\n<br />\n1.信佛/學佛有咩著數同缺點?<br />\n<br />\n2.佛家思想是否厭世?<br />\n<br />\n3.人人都應該學佛?<br />\n<br />\n4.佛所教授的道理正確嗎?"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T22:34:52.000Z","msg":"佛教咁無生產力又無乜建樹都好?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T22:39:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一切都是虛妄，都是貪嗔癡"},{"pid":"5d0319b1ab3bad3b2723a419a14f19d14d76a49b","tid":635873,"uid":182863,"like":1